DB::SQL::Migrations
       DB::SQL::Migrations - Perl extension to apply migrations from a directory

SYNOPSIS
         use DB::SQL::Migrations;
         my $migrator = DB::SQL::Migrations->new( dbh => $some_db_handle,
                                                  migrations => $some_path,
          )

         $migrator->apply();

DESCRIPTION
       Run a number of small SQL scripts

